WEBVTT

00:00.064 --> 00:01.589
Previously
on "Devious Maids"...

00:01.624 --> 00:03.772
Your son supported himself
for the last two years

00:03.807 --> 00:05.284
by selling drugs.

00:05.319 --> 00:08.167
Eddie was doing some business
with some trust fund brats.

00:08.203 --> 00:09.544
There was this one kid.

00:09.579 --> 00:11.263
The second Eddie's back was
turned, Flora was all over him.

00:11.298 --> 00:12.459
He's over there.

00:12.494 --> 00:14.001
Remi Delatour?

00:14.036 --> 00:16.265
Phillipe Delatour,
what are you up to?

00:16.300 --> 00:18.847
I wish I had been a better
husband to you. Oh.

00:18.882 --> 00:20.985
Well, just know
you can trust me.

00:21.020 --> 00:22.113
I do trust you.

00:22.148 --> 00:23.318
So I want to introduce you
to someone.

00:23.352 --> 00:24.519
Carmen, I want you
to meet Scott...

00:24.537 --> 00:26.121
My boyfriend.

00:26.155 --> 00:28.490
I saw our reflection
in the glass,

00:28.524 --> 00:30.659
and we looked like
bad people.

00:30.693 --> 00:32.527
Rosie, don't you want
to be with me?

00:32.545 --> 00:33.912
You made a vow
to your wife.

00:33.963 --> 00:36.298
We can't go around
breaking the rules. It's bad.

00:36.332 --> 00:38.466
Taylor and I are going
to have a baby.

00:38.501 --> 00:40.535
Are you going to be okay?

00:40.553 --> 00:41.536
Oh, my God.

00:41.554 --> 00:44.222
Michael! Oh, no.

00:44.257 --> 00:46.641
Somebody get a knife!

00:46.676 --> 00:47.926
Please come back to me.

00:47.977 --> 00:49.895
Please come back to me,
baby.

00:49.929 --> 00:52.180
I'm so sorry.
I'm sorry for everything.

01:00.022 --> 01:01.656
You listen to me, Howard.

01:01.691 --> 01:04.860
My last movie grossed
over $300 million,

01:04.894 --> 01:08.613
which means I want back end.
Merchandising.

01:08.664 --> 01:10.899
Perks coming out of my ass.

01:10.917 --> 01:12.233
And if you can't
get this for me,

01:12.251 --> 01:14.235
I will find an agent who can!

01:14.253 --> 01:15.620
Do you get what I'm saying?

01:15.671 --> 01:17.455
You moronic squib?!

