01:34.673 --> 01:36.791
Hey.
I just put the baby down.

01:36.825 --> 01:39.961
He's probably still awake
if you want to check on him.

01:41.663 --> 01:42.714
Mrs. Peri?

01:42.765 --> 01:44.632
Where's Spence?

01:44.666 --> 01:47.352
He left for New York this morning.

01:48.637 --> 01:51.055
Oh. Right.

01:51.106 --> 01:52.974
Are you okay?

01:53.008 --> 01:55.843
Oh, Rosie.

01:55.861 --> 01:59.480
Mrs. Peri, what is it?

01:59.514 --> 02:02.784
I was driving home...

02:02.818 --> 02:04.902
And this man just came
out of nowhere.

02:04.953 --> 02:07.688
And I tried to swerve,
but he was right in front of me.

02:07.706 --> 02:09.857
Are you saying
you hit someone?

02:09.875 --> 02:11.626
There was an accident.

02:11.660 --> 02:14.829
- Is he okay?
- I don't know.

02:14.863 --> 02:17.382
What did
the paramedics say?

02:17.416 --> 02:20.034
- Paramedics?
- From the ambulance.

02:22.054 --> 02:23.421
Oh, my God.

02:23.472 --> 02:26.424
You didn't call
an ambulance?

02:26.475 --> 02:28.542
I panicked. I just had
to get out of there.

02:28.560 --> 02:30.178
So you didn't stop
to help him?

02:30.212 --> 02:33.181
I can't afford
a scandal right now!

02:33.215 --> 02:36.401
I'm in negotiations
with Paramount!

02:36.435 --> 02:38.552
Where did this happen?

02:38.570 --> 02:39.854
Mulholland.

02:39.888 --> 02:41.939
Just past Coldwater. Why?

02:41.990 --> 02:43.658
I have to go check on him.

02:43.692 --> 02:44.776
Okay.

02:44.827 --> 02:46.110
Okay, that's good.

02:46.161 --> 02:47.662
But don't tell him
about me.

02:47.696 --> 02:49.080
I won't.

02:49.114 --> 02:51.899
But I will have to
call 9-1-1.

02:51.917 --> 02:53.835
- Rosie?
- Hmm?

02:53.869 --> 02:55.787
What if he's dead?

02:55.838 --> 02:57.004
You better get down
on your knees

02:57.039 --> 02:58.122
and pray to God he's not.

03:01.841 --> 03:04.762
That was not a suggestion.

03:12.788 --> 03:18.788
